  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Quantity Surveyor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Communicate with the management and sub-contractors on the adjustments to cost estimates.</li>\n  <li>Conduct the negotiations during the course of the project in order to ensure issues are resolved.</li>\n  <li>Assist to control project scope to meet project objectives in order to enhance project deliverables and key work activities.</li>\n  <li>Develop cost reduction strategies to enhance the overall value of the project.</li>\n  <li>Monitor project costs to ensure the objectives of the project are achieved in accordance to building contract law.</li>\n  <li>Assist to on compliance with standards.</li>\n  <li>Prepare tender and contract documents in accordance to the building and construction regulations.</li>\n  <li>Prepare the cost analysis for the project in order to ensure the overall value is enhanced.</li>\n  <li>Provide advice on contractual claims so that the project scope is managed.</li>\n</ul>",
